      "Generate videos using Veo, Seedance, Wan, and OmniHuman models with text or image prompts",
      "Call LLMs like Claude, Gemini, and Kimi through the OpenRouter integration",
      "Perform web search using Tavily and Exa search APIs from the command line",
      "Automate Twitter/X operations including posting tweets, sending DMs, and following users",
      "Upload local files (images, audio, video) as inputs to cloud AI models automatically"
